      </div>
      <div class="who-iam-text flex flex-col gap-2 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-ink leading-snug">I illuminate more than just interfaces</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-[1.8]">I spent <b>5 years</b> in the <b>banking and government-tech</b> spaces not just shipping screens, but also <b>redesigning organizational processes</b>, <b>building design governance</b>, and <b>mentoring</b> juniors and interns who all became confident designers themselves today!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- School card -->
    <div class="card-books who-iam-card flex flex-col items-center gap-4 pt-6 pb-6 px-6 border border-border-custom rounded-[10px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out cursor-default mt-6">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0">
        <svg width="72" height="72" viewBox="0 0 72 72" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <style>
            @keyframes lean {
              0%   { transform: rotate(0deg); }
              35%  { transform: rotate(7.83deg); }
              65%  { transform: rotate(7.83deg); }
              100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            }
            .left-book {
              transform-origin: 34.5px 63px;
              animation: lean 2.4s cubic-bezier(0.45, 0, 0.55, 1) infinite;
            }
          </style>
