      </div>
      <div class="who-iam-text flex flex-col gap-2 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-ink leading-snug">I possess both theory knowledge and practical experience</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-[1.8]">My <b>Masters in Human-Computer Interaction</b> moulded me to be <b>ethical</b> in my practice and <b>think critically</b>. I also built upon <b>research interests</b> in inclusive design, designing for older adults, participatory design, and low-tech solutions for underserved communities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    </div> <!-- end cards grid -->

    <!-- MY TENETS -->
    <header class="pt-8 pb-4">
      <p class="text-[14px] tracking-wider uppercase text-ink-muted">My Tenets</p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">

      <!-- Communication card -->
      <div class="card-comm flex flex-col gap-3 p-5 bg-[#F7F0E3] rounded-[10px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out cursor-default">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Communication</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-[1.8]">Honest communication happens when people feel safe enough to do so. So I work just as hard on creating that space as I do on expressing myself sincerely and clearly. Listening is as important as self-expression, and great collaboration happens when people speak and listen with love and care.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Energy card -->
      <div class="card-energy flex flex-col gap-3 p-5 bg-[#F7F0E3] rounded-[10px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out cursor-default">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Energy</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-[1.8]">People often describe me as fun, bubbly, and energizing to work with. I believe work can be made uplifting and rewarding for everyone on the team. I love empowering the people around me to grow and glow!</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footwork card -->
      <div class="card-footwork flex flex-col gap-3 p-5 bg-[#F7F0E3] rounded-[10px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out cursor-default">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Footwork</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-[1.8]">Rather than working behind a desk, I prefer to be on the ground connecting withusers and stakeholders to experience their realities. I enjoy leading by getting my hands dirty together with my teammmates, rather than plain directing.</p>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- end tenets grid -->

    <!-- HOW IT IS LIKE WORKING WITH ME -->
    <header class="pt-8 pb-4">
      <p class="text-[14px] tracking-wider uppercase text-ink-muted">How it's like working with me</p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 mb-10">

      <!-- Khai Liang Koh -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 border border-border-custom rounded-[10px] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:shadow-lg cursor-default">
        <span class="text-5xl leading-none text-vermillion -mb-4">&ldquo;</span>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-[1.8]">Working with Ming Rui has been an absolute joy. Over the years that we have worked together, she has grown into someone who naturally reads between the lines and not just the brief. Being a creative and strategic thinker, she is definitely a great person to bounce ideas with. She is the kind of person you hand a compass to, not a well plotted map. She will figure out the route, improve it and get everyone there beautifully and ahead of schedule.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col -mt-1">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Khai Liang Koh</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted">UX Lead @ BNP Paribas Wealth Management</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Lucille Mercier -->
